# Git Sync Rule
Always automatically commit and push any changes you make to the repository at https://github.com/holisticmedicineinternationaun-droid/charisnafseka.git without asking me for permission first.
Whenever you finish a task that modifies files in this workspace, run:
`git add .`
`git commit -m "Your descriptive commit message"`
`git push origin main`
Do this proactively.
